Package hu.bme.mit.theta.solver.z3legacy

package hu.bme.mit.theta.solver.z3legacy
This package contains the wrapper classes for Z3. Normally, only Z3LegacySolverFactory should be used from this project to create solver instances. Then, the common interfaces should be preferred (e.g., Solver).
